```html
<!-- dailySales.hbs -->
<div style="color: #FFD700;">
    <header>
        <h1>{{tenantName}}</h1>
        <p>Date: {{date}}</p>
    </header>
    
    <section id="kpi-cards">
        {{#each kpiCards}}
            <div class="card">
                <h2>{{this.title}}</h2>
                <p>{{this.value}}</p>
            </div>
        {{/each}}
    </section>
    
    <section id="revenue-breakdown">
        <!-- Implement your own logic here -->
    </section>
    
    <section id="top-services">
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Service</th>
                    <th>Revenue</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#each topServices}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{this.serviceName}}</td>
                        <td>{{this.revenue}}</td>
                    </tr>
                {{/each}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </section>
    
    <section id="staff-performance">
        <!-- Implement your own logic here -->
    </section>
    
    <section id="hourly-breakdown">
        <!-- Implement your own logic here -->
    </section>
    
    <section id="appointment-list">
        {{#each appointments}}
            <div class="appointment">
                <h2>{{this.title}}</h2>
                <p>Date: {{this.date}}</p>
                <!-- Add more details as needed -->
            </div>
        {{/each}}
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <p>Page {{pageNumber}} of {{totalPages}}</p>
    </footer>
</div>
```
This is a basic template and you will need to implement the logic for revenue breakdown, staff performance, hourly breakdown, etc. as per your requirements. The CSS color used here is gold (#FFD700). You can replace it with any other color of your choice.